A stakeholder register lists all stakeholders with their involvement level and communication method.
| Stakeholder        | Role               | Interest | Influence | Engagement           |
| ------------------ | ------------------ | -------- | --------- | -------------------- |
| Business Owners    | Primary users      | High     | High      | Feedback meetings    |
| Store Managers     | Daily users        | High     | High      | Demo reviews         |
| Warehouse Managers | Inventory handlers | Medium   | Medium    | Workflow discussions |
| System Admin       | Manages access     | High     | High      | Security meetings    |
| Customers          | End beneficiaries  | Medium   | Low       | Indirect feedback    |
| Suppliers          | Stock providers    | Medium   | Low       | Forecast sharing     |
| Project Team       | Developers         | High     | Medium    | Regular meetings     |
| Course Instructor  | Evaluator          | Medium   | High      | Reviews              |
